		<Placemark id="0C734745E640214C7E68">
			<name>Tengiz, Drilling oil filed (CPC blend)</name>
			<description><![CDATA[<p style="margin: 0px 0px 16.4px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 16.4px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 16.43px;">One of the</span></span></b></span><br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 21px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 21px;">largest oil fields in the world</span></span></b></span><br></p><ul style="list-style-type: disc;"><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">Discovered: 1979 (Soviet era)</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">Production: ~600,000–700,000 barrels/day</span></span></span><br></li></ul><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(128, 128, 128); min-height: 13.8px;"><br></p><div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Oil is extracted from deep reservoirs<br></div><div>* Sent to processing plants (CPF – Central Processing Facilities)<br></div><div>* Gas and sulfur removed (very important at Tengiz)<br></div><div>* Oil is stabilized (made safe for transport)<br></div><div><br></div><div>👉 Then:<br></div><div><br></div><div>* It enters gathering pipelines<br></div><div>* Flows to the CPC pipeline inlet<br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div><p style="margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 21px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 21px;">🔹 Extremely rich but technically complex</span></span></b></span><br></p><ul style="list-style-type: disc;"><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">Very high reservoir pressure</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">High sulfur content (H₂S gas)</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">Requires advanced processing</span></span></span><br></li></ul><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(128, 128, 128); min-height: 13.8px;"><br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 21px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 21px;">🔹 Operated by:</span></span></b></span><br></p><ul style="list-style-type: disc;"><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">Chevron (major stakeholder)</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">With partners:</span></span></span><br></li><ul style="list-style-type: circle;"><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">ExxonMobil</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">KazMunayGas</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">Lukoil</span></span></span><br></li></ul></ul><p style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(128, 128, 128); min-height: 13.8px;"><br></p><p style="margin: 0px 0px 14.9px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><b><span class="font" style="font-family: TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 18px;">⚙️ What happens there</span></span></b></span><br></p><ul style="list-style-type: disc;"><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">Oil is extracted and partially processed</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">Stabilized crude is sent into the CPC pipeline</span></span></span><br></li><li style="margin: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;"><span style="font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-kerning: none;"><span class="font" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><span class="size" style="font-size: 20px;">Then transported ~1,500 km to the Black Sea</span></span></span><br></li></ul><div><br></div>]]></description>
